To install & Customize the software first

1. edit main.py to adjust the programs arguments and if you would like to replace my api key with yours
2. edit setup.sh and review the commands and arguments at the topp ensure to edit the app directory varible to match where the program should install to .
    the setup.sh file will install a startup service to automaticly startup the program on boot delete the relevant commands in the script if you wish to remove this feature.
    it will also install the required packages and setup a venv for the program to run. 
3. Run setup.sh this will run the install commands.  the  service should then be running at port 1991